            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25607088/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25607088/" class="">第554页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/61466978/" class=" " title="大胡子★约瑟">大胡子★约瑟</a>
                (日行一善)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25607088">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">思维可以认识存在，这根本上仍是由于存在本身是思维＜小逻辑＞：＂真理是思维内容与其自身相符＂</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-06 12:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                思维可以认识存在，这根本上仍是由于存在本身是思维＜小逻辑＞：＂真理是思维内容与其自身相符＂
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

